snippet.textDisplay:
Suhos’ voice is so calm and beautiful. The lyric is wonderful and it is not just a mass-produced album, but it is made full of love and hard work.

I never gave Suho attention because there were other members that were much more interesting to me, but with this album, he just stole everyone's heart.

We are going threw tough times and it is hard to show our love to him at the moment, but he shows how much he loves us. He did a Privat meet and greet and facetimed with Exo-ls, so the last thing that we can do is str*am and buy his album.

Suho is a great leader and deserves everything he wants in the world.
snippet.textOriginal:
Suhos’ voice is so calm and beautiful. The lyric is wonderful and it is not just a mass-produced album, but it is made full of love and hard work.

I never gave Suho attention because there were other members that were much more interesting to me, but with this album, he just stole everyone's heart.

We are going threw tough times and it is hard to show our love to him at the moment, but he shows how much he loves us. He did a Privat meet and greet and facetimed with Exo-ls, so the last thing that we can do is str*am and buy his album.

Suho is a great leader and deserves everything he wants in the world.
